 # End-to-End Azure Data Engineering & Power BI Analytics Project

## ðŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project demonstrates a complete end-to-end data engineering pipeline using Azure services and Power BI. 

Raw sales data is ingested into Azure Data Lake Storage Gen2, transformed using Azure Synapse Serverless SQL, converted into Parquet format for performance optimization, processed using Spark Pool for advanced analytics, and finally visualized using an interactive Power BI dashboard.

This project showcases cloud data storage, transformation, analytics, and business intelligence reporting.

