##  Technology Stack

- Azure Data Lake Storage Gen2
- Azure Synapse Analytics (Serverless SQL)
- Spark Pool
- Parquet File Format
- Power BI Desktop

---

##  Project Workflow

###  1 â€“ Store Raw Data in ADLS Gen2
Raw sales data is uploaded and stored in Azure Data Lake Storage Gen2 to enable scalable and secure cloud storage.

###  2 â€“ Data Transformation using Synapse Serverless SQL
Serverless SQL Pool is used to query and transform raw data without provisioning dedicated infrastructure.

###  3 â€“ Convert Data to Parquet Format
Transformed data is converted into Parquet format to improve query performance and reduce storage size using columnar compression.

###  4 â€“ Advanced Analytics using Spark Pool
Spark Pool is used for advanced data processing and analytics on structured datasets.

###  5 â€“ Data Visualization using Power BI
An interactive Sales Revenue Dashboard is created in Power BI including:
- KPI Card (Total Revenue)
- Category-wise Revenue Bar Chart
- Revenue Distribution Pie Chart
- Interactive Slicer Filters
- Summary Table with Totals

